# Web3Forms access key — powers the contact + free-audit inquiry forms.
# Get a free key (no signup required) at https://web3forms.com:
#   1. Enter your inbox email (makomarketing0@gmail.com)
#   2. The access key is emailed to you instantly
#   3. Copy it into .env.local as the value below, then restart the dev server
# This key is safe to expose in the browser — it only routes submissions to your inbox.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
